{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"kYVvIrc2ZBNxaE7rztQ0H","title":"Lecture 7","desc":"","updated":1634529659508,"created":1634529035499,"custom":{},"fname":"courses.Semester 5.Embedded Systems.Lecture 7","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"1881d2a0564861576b46d82d741da11c","links":[],"anchors":{"avr-interfacing-with-7-segment-leds":{"type":"header","text":"AVR Interfacing with 7 segment LEDs","value":"avr-interfacing-with-7-segment-leds","line":9,"column":0,"depth":2},"leds":{"type":"header","text":"LEDs","value":"leds","line":11,"column":0,"depth":2},"7-segment-leds":{"type":"header","text":"7-Segment LEDs","value":"7-segment-leds","line":21,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"a1PatlsCiz7PYsL111lFm","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"lecture-7\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#lecture-7\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Lecture 7</h1>\n<h2 id=\"avr-interfacing-with-7-segment-leds\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#avr-interfacing-with-7-segment-leds\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>AVR Interfacing with 7 segment LEDs</h2>\n<h2 id=\"leds\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#leds\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>LEDs</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><img src=\"/notes/assets/images/2021-10-18-09-21-36.png\"></li>\n<li>Basically, whenever an electron tranverse from lower energy state to higher, it requires energy.</li>\n<li>Whenever it traverse from higher energy state to lower, it emits energy in the form of light.</li>\n<li>This is basic principle of LEDs.</li>\n<li>We use semiconductors for it. It has some bandgaps which emit light of particular frequency and as a result emit light of particular color.</li>\n<li>Connections\n<ul>\n<li><img src=\"/notes/assets/images/2021-10-18-09-25-22.png\"></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"7-segment-leds\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#7-segment-leds\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>7-Segment LEDs</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Common anode\n<ul>\n<li><img src=\"/notes/assets/images/2021-10-18-09-26-44.png\"></li>\n<li>Logic 0 means that portion of led will be turned on.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Common Cathode\n<ul>\n<li><img src=\"/notes/assets/images/2021-10-18-09-29-44.png\"></li>\n<li>Logic 1 means that portion of led will be turned on.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"GL4YoVrbDUHLnf946YtXV","title":"Curated Notes","desc":"","updated":1630150480330,"created":1629975412335,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"59326d3738fbbdf94df0792937dea389","links":[],"anchors":{},"children":["3ONxZ3Khb7nFPdLxlV1ib","Jq5ki9jf1QLTdc3DYLRW4","t5S98zYhQcXKMjbqBsVGg","Z2JlSyF7TPv3hFanVQhJd"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\n\n\nYou have reached the home page of my curated notes. I am a third year student pursuing Computer Science and Engineering at Ahmedabad University.\n\nFeel free to use this resource to its best potential and reach out to me on [Linkedin](https://www.linkedin.com/in/sameep-vani/) and do checkout my [GitHub](https://github.com/Sameep1234)\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true},"version":5,"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":false,"leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNote":{"initialValue":"templates"},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"copyNoteLink":{},"templateHierarchy":"template"},"workspace":{"dendronVersion":"0.100.0","vaults":[{"fsPath":"vault"}],"journal":{"dailyDomain":"daily","name":"journalc","dateFormat":"y